reviews.review_text: nice audience tape! 1989 was a hot year for live GD...Great setlist, especially set 2!

Brent I was at this show, and many other late 80's Bay Area shows as well. Hearing Brent's voice on 'We Can Run' still gives me a tight feeling in my chest and throat, all these years later. Miss that guy...
